SE-dcc3cba5-1fe0-48a9-9815-a2f420c956b4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">구축하는 것은 무척 힘든 일입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-94e1797f-c527-4d1f-aa7e-9c6fc2ba8ede\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fab636ef-5768-4e31-aea2-1f87813eaf34\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e4820460-d9f1-4ac1-a5cb-6b57b7e815ae\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e31f9baa-e0f5-436c-9cb6-05578b47b5b0\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">비용뿐 아니라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-85092f20-064b-49c7-80b5-407273476f47\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6f66e865-23b3-4db4-be07-183478a9dd7c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">납기, 그리고 개발의 어려움이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-93c0e938-a993-4833-893a-eda779b225b7\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c897829d-7556-47df-9d9c-aae664a085af\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0359b884-3f2f-4341-bd1b-4a1473089abb\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-33b34234-d8f5-4dcc-a83c-fb6f08470c41\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1559a119-b325-499b-924e-e797ae1c2541\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b79049f6-3b81-4203-85c2-84d40ea01a5c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f581336d-b879-4d4b-bab0-7b9d8bcb9e11\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cee11139-a5c7-469f-986b-0fe69b8da4f8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음과 같은 개발 진행을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-46be076d-ce61-4897-a0b4-cc0116855035\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ed0aabd2-e87c-4cab-b9f4-ca395db1e255\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">추진 중에 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8e7d1656-9f26-4f27-b511-05493f64c515\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0a48fcb9-ba16-46bd-b025-9b4ac420a48b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f471cde9-60aa-40be-aebb-24a2acc30fdd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dfb93410-f49a-410b-9593-6cda2daaffd1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>API 연동 개발</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7096ad25-093f-47a6-a03d-8dd103594c97\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4e0ba4cc-2a2d-4646-a6e8-d13c4ca2dd5d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">API 연동을 통해 3D 에디터를 개발하려고 합니다. 에디터를 자체적으로 개발하는 것은 무척 어려운 일입니다. 이는 수억 원이 소요될 뿐 아니라 기간으로도 무척 오래 걸리는 작업입니다. 그래서 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 API 연동을 통해 에디터 개발을 진행 중에 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-223b1aeb-c521-4054-9010-0525a13db1b9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-db7202a7-6040-4ec5-a46a-e093a5bfdff6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ba78a5e9-7a29-4855-9a83-1db06c6623c7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a29da121-2a31-4d79-b954-0cabe4e7dd32\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음은 활발히 진행 중인 몇 가지 글로벌 에디터 사이트입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-611abac4-de58-4614-9667-5ad0127c3430\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7ab9a869-e3ab-43e9-bf37-f0d964b5fe5c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4198382c-b324-4023-98c7-83262a9fb99d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-daa02276-471e-4d2d-baf6-4e8914cce9b9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-daa02276-471e-4d2d-baf6-4e8914cce9b9\", \"link\": \"https://apidemo.pacdora.com/index.html\"}' data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://apidemo.pacdora.com/index.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://apidemo.pacdora.com/index.html</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-07ea6c21-bcef-4a45-8317-643c8f3573a4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-12b7a430-2f6d-4398-8705-d82220aff49c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5a3853d9-6842-47a0-abff-55865e5f1fe6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a189ec73-686c-477c-9d1b-51eee564a49f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e82c5dc0-4286-432c-8da5-8d9a612cc5f3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-e82c5dc0-4286-432c-8da5-8d9a612cc5f3\", \"link\": \"https://www.pack.ly/en\"}' data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://www.pack.ly/en\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pack.ly/en</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ceba8bcb-c7c1-4a4b-af2b-6898b96919cc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b4a293d3-3a16-411a-b96b-d1232f22bf79\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3c776344-b271-4c81-9b95-70332746ccaa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7172c2c3-c2d6-491c-8116-0cf51c4b55e2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3b1f5f30-46fb-426b-a4ed-9c17ad079849\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">물론 모든 패키지 에디터 회사와 api 연동을 할 수 있는 것은 아닙니다. 저희는 가능한 충분한 검토 기간을 두고 개발에 착수 중에 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c7385dec-b1e2-4052-addb-b3d840f1995e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-eca05c33-decb-455b-9e7e-2f4320030b3c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6c85be46-f387-4321-9925-c2650526cf71\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0b531c2d-0081-4f56-baa3-fb2863f24cbc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4e08268f-f396-4751-8cc7-119eb3f96178\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8294ce46-f3bb-43d3-be99-b1fa22ed15bc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4483dd99-373c-4e5d-aef4-2b3c7f7007c0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223896020613#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
